item.dc:creator: @poopler40 poopler40
item.description:
@poopler40 wrote:

[quote=“amy_webb, post:2, topic:534384”]Amazing work as per usual, are you making npc for a specific project or just for personal entertainment?

Thanks. I’m trying to get my own project going with my own models, as i wanna make a server so im learning to code java so its going to be a long process. These are just the beginning of the the four main factions. Humans, Elves, Dwarves, and Justicars.

The only problem i have with the first one is the spikes missing on the opposite leg, the whole model looks symmetrical except for that one area which throws the model off balance.

lol i just noticed that myself i forgot the mirror the spikes over, i will fix it when i get the chance.

With the elves you might want to change the pant colour, it seems too close to the skin colour which makes it look like it’s their skin.

I thought about the this and i was think to change the skin tone too a more golden yellow like the high elves in Skyrim.[/quote]
